Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Saionji-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go and get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:03:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, if I sleep now, we'll never make the deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...don't we go outside for some fresh air?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We're taking a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys should get some rest if you need it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything happens, call my cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be pretty much fine for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hand feels like ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't keep your room so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I turn off the air conditioning, you guys sweat all over the manuscripts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that stress can cause your body temperature to fall, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, about that new job you were mentioning recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's worth taking if it'll cause a drop in the quality of your current work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never been very strong, physically or mentally, Maa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're just now making enough to put food on your plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't think there's any need to get greedy with money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The public's current interest in my work could easily disappear come next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:05:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's always a new generation of artists hitting the scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And people can grow bored with your work just like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're way too pessimistic, Maa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You have ink on your face again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a girl, so you should really{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a manga artist!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to bother you all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be bothered to go to work...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:05:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you come out when I called you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. It's too hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that cool you down?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.26,0:06:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we make your lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, give me a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin's summer holidays have started.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We make her lunch together in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and then she goes to a daycare centre.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to visit Granddad's grave next Saturday?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost time for the Bon Festival,\Nafter all, and your flowers should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:53.26,Note,,0,0,0,,TL Note: A Japanese holiday when it is customary to honour the deceased spirits of your ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You don't want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The bellflowers haven't bloomed yet, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, right. I guess they'll take a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about we buy some from a florist this time? We'll take yours once they've bloomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that Granddad would be happy if you brought him bellflowers that you grew.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But just having you there would make him the happiest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If Rin weren't here, I doubt I'd be thinking of Granddad like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan! Rin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Kouki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You'll mess it all up if you move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:07:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is your hair so fine, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we're going to be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.89,0:08:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi, how many more days?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,About ten, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Found one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A cicada shell!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A shell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, this is nostalgic...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a ton of them in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop shaking them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out for cars!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been here lots of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,With Granddad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I guess Granny's grave is here too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Granddad's granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny and Granddad had a child, my mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, she had me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! So your mum is Granddad's daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That means I'm your mother's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! I shouldn't have pointed her in that direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all wet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That vase...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Masako-san had one just like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell? But she didn't even come to the funeral...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin, I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull out some of the weeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who goes to visit a grave with a guy, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Woof!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?! What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were some sort of stalker...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We happened to come to the graveyard after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It was really just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought I should let you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...that Rin's here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.88,0:11:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She's at Granddad's grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin's very dear to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:11:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,so I don't really think very fondly of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't really care about what's going on in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no intention of forcing the two of you to meet again, unless she wants it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you want to tell me so badly that you chased after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask if you wanted to at least secretly get a look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to clean the grave, light some incense and go home,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,so we'll probably be around for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, Rin's waiting for me. I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just be doing what we came here to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin... Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you waiting long?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I had something to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you waiting long?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Not too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you getting so worked up for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not being weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Plant them there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not a baby any more...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood ties are amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.47,0:13:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. She looks just like you, Maa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:14:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That back...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.11,0:14:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She's pretty cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That sense of distance...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so much like Souichi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That was really a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess coincidences like this only pop up when it's almost Obon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She turns seven today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Learning about your daughter was a shock, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.39,0:14:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but I thought maybe the guy was your ex-boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't have a single brain cell in that head of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Though that could change in another half-century.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Half... century?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's logical to assume that that guy was her boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi? You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's not such a bad thing, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.18,0:15:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,For someone madly in love, it didn't\Ntake her long to find somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we go to Granddad's?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's close by, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... But it's not Granddad's house any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is somebody living there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nobody's living there, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It belongs to my uncle on my mother's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddhist altar is there too, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll ask my uncle if we can at least take a look around the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:15:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:15:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to take them up on that job, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be okay, Maa-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave her up for the sake of my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You already are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're working harder than anyone needs to!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.17,0:16:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to work so hard that I can't even\Nremember what I had for dinner the night before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on. Even I forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't forget all of those things...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little further!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just the same as it used to be, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've changed so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The bellflowers are gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The dirt is gone, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Those bellflowers were so important to Granddad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he didn't mean to just yank them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.17,0:17:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Even my uncle could tell you Granddad's favourite flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:18:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But when Winter comes, they wither.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably didn't know that they bloom again in Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And these stones...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't spread them around,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the area will become overrun with weeds before you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad we got Rin's fragrant olive tree out...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.37,0:18:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That was lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But luckily, we have bellflowers for Granddad at our house, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe things changing isn't always a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But that grave will always be Granddad's grave, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A chocolate cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Saionji-sensei, can you do a final check?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You really seem like you're pushing yourself too hard this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When you say things like that, my hands stop working properly, so stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll finish it, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.82,0:21:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi! All of the nighttime stalls are going to close!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.28,0:21:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like Granddad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:21:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's Kouki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We were supposed to be meeting at the shrine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.88,0:22:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum's too slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.93,0:22:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not wearing a yukata?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.89,0:22:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't jump in one!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.10,0:22:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.10,0:22:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your mum?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.90,0:22:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she'd meet us at the shrine after she put on her yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.32,0:22:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go! The nighttime stalls will close!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi, look out for cars!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.87,0:22:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.00,0:22:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! It's hard to run in wooden clogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.67,0:22:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll carry you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.46,0:22:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:22:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You can carry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.73,0:22:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Tongue twisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.77,0:23:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The frogs matched three Pyocopyoco Pyocopyoco with six Pyocopyoco Pyocopyoco. {Kaeru pyokopyoko mi pyokopyoko awasete pyokopyoko mu pyokopyoko}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.40,0:23:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon, Rin here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.44,0:23:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A big typhoon is coming, so I went home with Kouki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.28,0:23:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I was scared at first, but then I got excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.66,0:23:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A typhoon is a bit mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.54,0:23:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The next story is "A Typhoon Has Come!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.21,0:23:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The neighbor's persimmon was eaten by a lot of costumers. {tonari no kaki wa yoku kyaku kuu kaki da}
